<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Understanding China's Folk Culture: New Student Photo Exhibit Opens at UCF</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Christine Dellert
		
		<span class="date">Nov. 19, 2008</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="http://news.ucf.edu/resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1615/en_US/sharon photo2 crop.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Sharon Weaver</p>
			
			<p>A gourd painter at the Huobali Festival Market in China displays his craft. </p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041e030fdf011daaca4445007df0">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
